    <item>
      <title>经合组织认为全球经济增长“喜忧参半”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/oecd-sees-mixed-picture-on-global-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织首席经济学家克莱尔·隆巴德利（Clare Lombardelli）从全球增长和通胀的角度讨论了该组织的中期经济前景。她还研究了美国对中国关税的潜在增加可能如何影响全球贸易和经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/oecd-sees-mixed-picture-on-global-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:11:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织经济学家表示，与欧洲相比，美国经济非常强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/us-economy-is-remarkably-strong-as-eu-weak-oecd-economist-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织首席经济学家克莱尔·隆巴德利表示，与欧洲相比，美国经济显示出“显着的实力”，欧洲各国近年来在紧缩的货币政策和能源价格飙升的冲击下陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/us-economy-is-remarkably-strong-as-eu-weak-oecd-economist-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中东战争损害了麦当劳的业绩，麦当劳的销售增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/mcdonald-s-sales-growth-slows-with-mideast-war-hurting-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦当劳公司第四季度的销售额未达到投资者的预期，原因是增长放缓，部分原因是受到中东冲突的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/mcdonald-s-sales-growth-slows-with-mideast-war-hurting-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
